author: ForceMagic
title: Nice simple racing car !
review:
Haha, I had so much fun with this car when I was young, it was definitivly the fastest one ;) 

It's a nice little car, not a lot of parts but some really nice like the Motor block and the Octan wing.

author: jsosse
title: Cool engine
review:
This set stands alone while in comparison to the ones alike. The only reason to that is its engine. Unlike others, it has one and a very cool one for such a small set, for all that matter. Others have not so ingenously desing engines, others none at all.

That, and of course the nice Octan wing, are the reasons why this is perhaps the best little race car among that era's.
